node.text: had an absolute blast surprising @_alyssa.mar with all of my Top Gift Picks from @fivebelow and a #fivebelow gift card!! Alyssa was diagnosed with leukemia 2 years ago and she also happens to be a huge fan ❤ special shout-out to @sloankettering and @alexslemonade for helping make this happen! #mskkids #alexslemonade #ad
